         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne, 26/9/76. ¶  ¶ The lichen collection, ¶  esteemed Professor, has safely arrived, and I am very pleased about it. — I now write just a few words to ask you to sign the enclosed documents, so ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">76.09.26a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Jean Müller</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Conservatoire et Jardin botanique, Geneva.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">Melbourne, 26/9/76.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Die Flechten Sammlung, geehrter Herr Professor, ist richtig angekommen, und ich habe mich recht darüber gefreuet. — Ich schreibe nun nur einige Worte, um Sie zu bitten, die beifolgenden Documente zu zeichnen, damit ich den Betrag des beigefügten Wechsels reclamieren kann.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Mit bestem Grusse,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne, 26/9/76.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The lichen collection,<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Hepp's exsiccatae, <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Die Flechten Europas</seg> (1853-67); see M to J. Müller, 24 February 1876.</p>
               </note> esteemed Professor, has safely arrived, and I am very pleased about it. — I now write just a few words to ask you to sign the enclosed documents, so that I can claim the amount of the enclosed draft.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">With best greetings</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
         </div>
      </body>
